@startuml IBM_datastax-cassandra-clickstream

actor User
participant "Next.js Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Redux Store" as Redux
participant "Next.js API Routes" as API
participant "clicks.service.js" as ClicksService
database "DSE/Cassandra" as Database

User -> Frontend : Browses products
Frontend -> API : GET /api/products
API -> Frontend : Return product data
Frontend -> ClicksService : trackPageBrowsing()
ClicksService -> Database : Insert page view data

User -> Frontend : Adds product to cart
Frontend -> Redux : Dispatch add to cart action
Redux -> API : POST /api/products (add to cart)
API -> ClicksService : addToCart()
ClicksService -> Database : Insert add to cart event

User -> Frontend : Views clickstream history
Frontend -> API : GET /api/history
API -> ClicksService : getActivity()
ClicksService -> Database : Query clickstream data
Database --> ClicksService : Return clickstream data
ClicksService --> API : Process data
API --> Frontend : Return processed history
Frontend --> User : Display clickstream history

User -> Frontend : Signs in
Frontend -> API : POST /api/auth/[...nextauth]
API -> Frontend : Return authentication result
Frontend -> Redux : Update user state

@enduml